graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack Provider Ragas"
        direction TB
        subgraph InlineMode["Inline Mode (In-Process)"]
            InlineEval[RagasEvaluatorInline]
            InlineLLM[LlamaStackInlineLLM<br/>BaseRagasLLM wrapper]
            InlineEmbed[LlamaStackInlineEmbeddings<br/>BaseRagasEmbeddings wrapper]
            InlineEval -->|uses| InlineLLM
            InlineEval -->|uses| InlineEmbed
        end

        subgraph RemoteMode["Remote Mode (Kubeflow Pipelines)"]
            RemoteEval[RagasEvaluatorRemote]
            KFPClient[KFP Client]
            Pipeline[Pipeline Definition<br/>retrieve_data + run_ragas]
            RemoteEval -->|submits| KFPClient
            KFPClient -->|creates| Pipeline
        end

        Config[RagasConfig / KubeflowConfig<br/>Pydantic models]
        Compat[compat.py<br/>Llama Stack version abstraction]
        Config -.->|configures| InlineEval
        Config -.->|configures| RemoteEval
        Compat -.->|imports| InlineEval
        Compat -.->|imports| RemoteEval
    end

    Client[Client / User] -->|Eval API request| LlamaStackServer
    LlamaStackServer[Llama Stack Distribution Server<br/>8321/TCP] -->|delegates| InlineEval
    LlamaStackServer -->|delegates| RemoteEval

    InlineLLM -->|in-process| InferenceAPI[Llama Stack Inference API]
    InlineEmbed -->|in-process| InferenceAPI

    Pipeline -->|HTTP 8321| LlamaStackServer2[Llama Stack Server<br/>from KFP pods]
    Pipeline -->|HTTPS 443| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Results]

    RemoteEval -->|HTTPS 443| KFP[Kubeflow Pipelines API]
    RemoteEval -->|HTTPS 443| S3Read[S3 Storage<br/>Read Results]

    LlamaStackOp[Llama Stack Operator] -->|manages| LlamaStackServer

    style InlineEval fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style RemoteEval fill:#4a90e2,color:#fff
    style InlineLLM fill:#5ba3d9,color:#fff
    style InlineEmbed fill:#5ba3d9,color:#fff
    style KFPClient fill:#5ba3d9,color:#fff
    style Pipeline fill:#5ba3d9,color:#fff
    style Config fill:#9b59b6,color:#fff
    style Compat fill:#9b59b6,color:#fff
    style LlamaStackServer fill:#f5a623,color:#000
    style LlamaStackServer2 fill:#f5a623,color:#000
    style InferenceAPI fill:#7ed321,color:#000
    style KFP fill:#e8e8e8,color:#000
    style S3 fill:#e8e8e8,color:#000
    style S3Read fill:#e8e8e8,color:#000
    style LlamaStackOp fill:#7ed321,color:#000
    style Client fill:#f9f9f9,color:#000
